{
  "name": "Focused Miasma",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>By focusing your naturally disruptive odor you are able to sap another creature of its willpower.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Fermon alraun, odor of susceptibility.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> By spending a standard action to suppress your odor of susceptibility (provoking attacks of opportunity), you can narrow its effects into a miasma that targets only one creature within 20 feet, increasing its penalty to -2 while it is within this range. This is a mind-affecting effect and creatures that do not need to breathe are immune to its effects. Deactivating focused miasma is a swift action.</p>\n",
